rgin: 16px 0;">And moving on to =E2=80=9Cpicking off market makers=E2=80=99=
 stale quotes=E2=80=9D:</p><blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">[Carste=
n] Koerl came up with the idea for betandwin over one long night in 1996. I=
